rnd_lab

This project is a derivative fork of robot_lab:
https://github.com/fan-ziqi/robot_lab

The upstream project was originally authored by Ziqi Fan and is distributed
under the Apache License 2.0.

`rnd_lab`'s maintained scope is the non-4bar RND STEP humanoid reinforcement
learning environment, including its robot asset integration, Isaac Lab task
configuration, sim-to-real randomization, reward shaping, and training/play
workflow changes.

Other upstream robot environments may remain in the source tree for reference
or compatibility, but they are not the maintained target of this fork unless
explicitly documented otherwise.
